<img src=http://www.clan-donald.com/images/Severine%2024%20Banner.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uqwade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qwade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/01 10:05:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd question but...</span><hr size=1> You won't ever see all the wizards retired even though are numbers continue to drop.  I would be interested to see the numbers of people who would make wizards on a new non-split server though.   <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=10459><b>Qwade Starlifter</b></a><BR>
57th Gnome Evoker of Lanys T'vyl<BR>
<a href=http://www.seven-dreams.org/><i>Seven Dreams</i></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulenadaynastardew.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lenadayna Stardew</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/01 10:55:50 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=c:\windows\desktop\lena.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd question but...</span><hr size=1>    I think the others are right. They'd just make Hate and Sky walk on. They have demonstrated cluelessness, they are afraid to fix wizards for what amount to invalid reasons. Until they get some competition and Verant's pocketbook is hit, nothing will be done.<br>
  <br>
   They could care less about how much we complain until we stop giving them our money.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaitop.showPublicProfile?language=EN>daitop</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/01 11:11:44 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> retirements or boycotts...</span><hr size=1> Don't work since most people, like me, feel a greater loyalty to their friends and guildmates than to the wizard community.<br>
<br>
I'm not going to refuse a friend a port because my class is broken nor am I going to join with the other guild wizards in refusing to port to hate/sky unless the guild helps me raise a stink.<br>
<br>
What I am going to do is what many others have done.  I've started a rogue twink and I'm loving it.  I love watching the damage fly by almost faster than I can read it.  I now truly feel like the damage dealer the wiz should be...and ironically have more hps and ac...this was perhaps the biggest thing to yank my chain....wizards giving up all those hps and all that ac and defensive skills...for what?  Translocate?  <br>
<br>
I play my wizard now only for brief times to keep the xp bar moving (if only slightly) or for guild events.<br>
<br>
I've completely given up trying to get Verant to fix the class.  Whenever I see an idiotic post by Absor (and he's been on a roll lately) I always manage to stop myself somewhere between the eq home page andthe subject line of a response.<br>
